Subject: Unable to add non-ICT domain owners in 'resource owners'
Description: Hi, Within the 'resource owners' section, when i select to Add and owner manually, I can input the site that I want but when I get to 'select owners' I am only seeing 'ICT' domain. Whereas previously I could see multiple domains. I can therefore only security an owner in ICT domain which should not be the case. This is a new issue and I was able to select from our multiple domains in the past.
What_We_Know__c: Domains were missing in the "AuthSearchDomain" field in the "AccessInformationCenter.Service.exe.config" file
Solution_Comment__c:
Added non-ICT domains in the "AuthSearchDomain" field in the "AccessInformationCenter.Service.exe.config" file.
By default, it's located in the "C:Program FilesStealthbitsAccess Information Center" folder."
